FBIS3-22187 "jpten006___94050" JPRS-TEN-94-006 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Environmental Issues 8 MARCH 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA INDIA Agreement Reached With Brazil on Environmental Cooperation BK2202064794 Delhi Doordarshan Television Network in English 1630 GMT 21 Feb 94 BK2202064794 Delhi Doordarshan Television Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] India and Brazil are to cooperate in the fields of forestry, pollution control and waste management. This was announced after talks between the environment minister, Mr. Kamalnath, and his Brazilian counterpart, Mr. Rubens Ricupero, in New Delhi today. Mr. Ricupero offered Brazilian know-how for using alcohol as a substitute for petrol. He sought Indian assistance in environment audit.
